The article is a Presidential Memorandum issued by President Donald J. Trump. The memorandum is titled "Presidential Determination Pursuant to Section 303 of the Defense Production Act of 1950, as amended." In the memorandum, President Trump determines that the development and purchase of equipment and materials needed for alane fuel cells are essential to national defense. He states that without Presidential action, the United States industry cannot reasonably be expected to provide the capability for the production of alane fuel cells adequately and in a timely manner. The President authorizes and directs the Secretary of Defense to publish the memorandum in the Federal Register.